    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295810/extras/8abdf81b636fb5c1a8fb729170edb649.avif?t=1771930370\" width=631 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Remote Reaper: FPV Drone&quot; is a simulator that immerses the player in the role of an FPV combat drone operator in modern warfare. The player operates FPV drones using a remote control to strike enemy vehicles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remote Reaper: FPV Drone supports all popular controllers and gamepads, allowing pilots to train using a convenient control method!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RadioMaster</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DJI <u>FPV</u></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TBS</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BetaFPV</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Xbox</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PS</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remote Reaper: FPV Drone offers realistic controls via a controller and a simplified control mode that allows easy drone operation using a keyboard and mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295810/extras/7593fa1e073738b59d7764a29ee95572.poster.avif?t=1771930370\" width=576 height=325 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295810/extras/7593fa1e073738b59d7764a29ee95572.webm?t=1771930370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each enemy vehicle has weak spots. Your task is to identify these critical points and deliver precise strikes for effective enemy destruction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295810/extras/ab6ef974d4666af28923d02f57a9e212.poster.avif?t=1771930370\" width=576 height=325 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295810/extras/ab6ef974d4666af28923d02f57a9e212.webm?t=1771930370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will undertake various combat missions, including destroying enemy vehicles, locating, and striking high-value targets from the air.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in modern warfare, where success depends entirely on your skills and strategy. Precision and reaction speed are key factors for victory, while a well-planned tactic will allow you to dominate the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295810/extras/bcd0a76be134b676d0466247b64b14ae.poster.avif?t=1771930370\" width=576 height=325 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295810/extras/bcd0a76be134b676d0466247b64b14ae.webm?t=1771930370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's world is based on modern warfare concepts and incorporates the latest military technologies. Combat vehicles and advanced drones play crucial roles in various conflicts, allowing players to experience the real tension of military operations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295810/extras/d0514bc4abde0c811ce263f02236a641.poster.avif?t=1771930370\" width=576 height=325 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3295810/extras/d0514bc4abde0c811ce263f02236a641.webm?t=1771930370\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
